# jQuery video popup player
=========================

A jQuery video popup player plugin based on Abhinay Rathore's plugin for YouTube.

Original project homepage : [click here](http://lab.abhinayrathore.com/jquery_youtube/)

We have modified it in order to manage Vimeo and Dailymotion videos as well as YouTube ones as it did originally.
